description.text: this message file contains message for [name] package

msg.text: This device does not have a quadrant-based clock structure.
Clock preferences have quadrant specifications; however, this device does not have a quadrant-based clock structure; therefore, the quadrant clock specification will be ignored.
There is no primary Hspine available for signal $$s.
Due to no spare H-spine is available, this primary clock $$s will be routed as an ordinary net and may suffer from excessive delay or skew.

The driver of primary clock net $$s is not placed on one of the PIO sites dedicated for primary clocks. This primary clock will be routed to a H-spine through general routing resource and may suffer from excessive delay or skew.
There is no secondary Hspine available for signal $$s.
Due to no spare H-spine is available, this secondary clock $$s will be routed as an ordinary net and may suffer from excessive delay or skew.
The driver of secondary clock net $$s will be routed to clock tree through general routing resource and may suffer from excessive delay.

The driver of secondary clock net $$s is not placed on one of the PIO sites dedicated for secondary clocks. This secondary clock will be routed through general routing resource and may suffer from excessive delay or skew.
